description: Dynamic Route For CDN (DCDN) is a high-performance, reliable, and secure full site acceleration solution. This service aims to accelerate access to hybrid sites that use both dynamic and static resources. DCDN integrates multiple products and services, such as dynamic acceleration systems, smart static content caching, HTTPS, and operations security. You can use DCDN to both speed-up access and ensure the stability of your site.
